Looking at the Cart page, it looks like there's a form that submits the item AND the price!
I checked out the POST method in OWASP-ZAP and sure enough, URL-encoded was the same data.
I decoded it, changed the price to 0.00, encoded, and sent it as a new POST method, which yielded the flag!

